'''Zeison Sha Initiate armor''' was a type of light [[Armor/Legends|armored]] robe that was worn by Initiates of the [[Zeison Sha]]. It did not restrict in any way the [[Telekinesis/Legends|telekinetic]] [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force power/Legends|powers]] employed by its users, and was readily customizable.

